text: Że życie ma sens () is an album by Polish rapper Z.B.U.K.U. It contains 15 tracks. The official premiere took place on 16 October 2013. On 14 January 2015, the album was certified gold. The album features several fellow rappers: Rover, Leszek, Bezczel, Bonson, Jopel. == Track listing == # "Siema brat" – 5:09 # "HH rewolucja" – 3:29 # "Torreador bitów" – 3:38 # "To więcej niż muzyka" (feat.
